============================================
  Wolfe - A Reliable Job Management System
============================================

    I'm Winston Wolfe. I solve problems.  -- Pulp Fiction (1994)

Wolfe is a job management system.


Development Status
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Pre-Alpha.


