Bugs
~~~~

No bugs, of course. ;-)
But if you've found one or have an idea how to improve wolfe, feel
free to send a pull request on `github
<https://github.com/ndparker/wolfe>`_ or send a mail to
<wolfe-bugs@perlig.de>.


